Feline2::

She looked at HotRod. "You still have these..feelings?"
She wasn't sure what to say. With part of her past missing from her, 
she wasn't sure if she should continue or not. But for now, she would 
go with his words."Well, all I know is that, I remember you meaning 
something to me. But to what degree, I can't say. But if we loved 
each other," she looked down." I suppose I can try to love you, 
again."



--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, RoboRick007 <rfa007@h...> wrote:
> ::Hot Rod::
> 
> He stoped and turned to Feline, in a deserted hall.
> "Now where to start." He was silent for a minute.
> "You and me shared something big. I dont know how much you felt, 
but to
> me, you were the 'one'. We wanted to be together. I loved you."
> He stoped, the corrected himself.
> "I still do. I love you!"
